{
  "stem": "8786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somebody made-- twisted it around, because we were-- this was supposed to be-- originally supposed to be they are going for farm work in the country.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But somebody was mixing up these things and the big shots got those positions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were-- we were sent out-- outside of the country to the Russian [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] fire line, which is called a front, to the front.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's how we called it, the area which-- where the-- where the battles were, where the battles were fought, that was called the front.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jelsava we stayed not more than about-- we were doing some local work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every day we went out to the forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still met over there some boys, Gentile boys, with whom I went to high school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if I would have enough brain or guts, I would tell them, John, give me a place to hide.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But somehow we did not-- we didn't think of it that they are going to take my beautiful mother, who was 44, and my sister, one of them was 18, 19, 21, and 23, and my-- my brother, that they're going to take him and take him away to a slaughter house.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it somehow didn't penetrate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It couldn't-- we couldn't think of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- and I saw everybody was staying, so I stayed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But looking retroactively, I say to myself, I was a young kid, why shouldn't I-- why didn't I have enough brain or guts to hide someplace?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't-- and it was sometimes very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were many, many of them were caught and lost their life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What is the next question, please?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was asking you what type of work did you do at that forced labor point?",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
